entries.biography:
My name is Sopheaktra. I am a student in grade 8 at Pursat Secondary School. I live with my parents and my 2 brothers. My father is a policeman and my mother is a housewife.

Some of my favorite activities are playing sports, doing homework and reading books. I attend school at Sustainable Cambodia because I want to get better knowledge to support my studies at state school.&nbsp;
In the future, I want to become a policeman because I want to help protect my nation.
